latestPosts.caption:
Blessed to dress this face ♥️🧿 

Mehendi glam for my first ever friend and favoritest Human in the whole world ♥️ 🌎

Not going to say too much because you know what you mean to me 🥹♥️🧿

Lazy girl makeup hack …

Coping with 365 days of summer , using only blush for my look and some lip butter 

Done one side with my everyday @nudestix in ‘Cherry Blossom Babe’
Other side with @rarebeauty liquid blush in the shade ‘Worth’ 
(This is more intense for those with blush not lasting long enough issues ) 

Eyes - Again  @nudestix 

Lips - lip gutter from @simplynam.beauty 
Lip gloss - currently can’t do without @gisou

You don’t need to GRWM , just watch me get ready 🫠

Products I’ve used 

Base - Hollywood flawless filter @charlottetilbury 
Concealer - @narsissist obvs 
Setting powder - @charlottetilbury airbrush flawless 
Eyebrows - @benefitindia good poof brow pencil 
Blush - @rarebeauty 
Highlighter - @rarebeauty 
Mascara - @maybelline_ind non water proof cause I love my lashes 
Brown kajal - @simplynam.beauty 
Lip gloss - @gisou 
Lip butter - @simplynam.beauty
